revision.text:
'''2b Theatre Company''', stylized as the '''2b theatre company''', is a theatre company based in [[Halifax, Nova Scotia|Halifax]], [[Nova Scotia]].
== History == 2b was founded by a group of recent graduates and emerging artists in 1999 under the name "Bunnies in the Headlights Theatre." In 2004, Christian Barry and Anthony Black took over as artistic co-directors, and reinvented the company as 2b theatre.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.2btheatre.com/volunteer/team/history/|title=2b theatre companyHistory {{!}} 2b theatre company|website=www.2btheatre.com|access-date=2016-10-06}}</ref>
== Mandate == 2b theatre company strives to stimulate the mind and to awaken the spirit by producing theatre that is vital, innovative and challenging. Based in Halifax, Nova Scotia, 2b theatre company creates, develops, and presents works for the regional, national and international stages.
== Touring == While based in Halifax, 2b is a touring company. To date, 2b has toured to 40 cities in 10 countries on four continents.
List of cities visited by 2b:<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://thechronicleherald.ca/artslife/1212283-2b-productions-bound-for-edinburgh-fringe|title=2b productions bound for Edinburgh Fringe|date=2014-06-04|newspaper=The Chronicle Herald|access-date=2016-10-11}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.tata.com/media/releasesinside/World-class-performances-to-take-centre-stage-at-Tata-Literature-Live-The-Mumbai-LitFest|title=World-class performances to take centre stage at Tata Literature Live! The Mumbai LitFest via @tatacompanies|last=Tata.com|website=www.tata.com|access-date=2016-10-11}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.capacoa.ca/en/conference/past-conferences/2015-nov-culture-of-inclusion/delegate-list|title=2015 Delegate List|last=Administrator|website=www.capacoa.ca|access-date=2016-10-11}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.magneticnorthfestival.ca/about/past-festivals/|title=Past Festivals {{!}} Canada's Magnetic North Theatre Festival|newspaper=Canada's Magnetic North Theatre Festival|language=en-US|access-date=2016-10-11}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.memphisflyer.com/memphis/when-it-rains/Event?oid=4644250|title=When it Rains|last=225 S. Main|first=Memphis Downtown TN 38103|last2=35.13988;-90.05587|website=Memphis Flyer|access-date=2016-10-11|last3=901-529-4299|last4=location!|first4=Be the first to review this}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ice-storm-showcase.com/companies|title=CINARS presents ICE STORM SHOWCASE @ APAP 2016 {{!}} Companies List & Shows Details|last=Services|first=Leechee Web|website=www.ice-storm-showcase.com|access-date=2016-10-11}}</ref> {{div col|colwidth=22em}} * [[Aarhus]] * [[Albany, Western Australia]] * [[Antigonish, Nova Scotia|Antigonish]] * [[Auckland]] * [[Burnaby]] * [[Calgary]] * [[Charleston, South Carolina|Charleston]] * [[Chester, Nova Scotia|Chester]] * [[Cork (city)|Cork]] * [[Cow Head, Newfoundland and Labrador|Cow Head]] * Dartmouth * [[Denmark, South Carolina|Denmark]] * [[Edinburgh]] * [[Edmonton]] * [[F